en.title: FE Welcomes Canadian QP Wearer, Former Professional Football Player, Paul Swaby.
en.content: FE's QP is spreading throughout the world like wildfire! Photos show Canadian QP Wearer, former Professional Football Player, Paul Swaby, who is a motivational speaker and an author. Paul Swaby is currently working on his second book. His first book is titled "ONE PERCENT".
